    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe current implementation of the autocmds that the editorconfig sets up are not nested, meaning that if one has an autocmd to run :write, :update or equivalent, those auto command from the editor config plugin will not be run. Could be Either a user configurable option, or however the core team decides to implement it\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nBe able to apply the editorconfig features which rely on autocmds from user defined autcmd.",
